body:
@aaltay reviews are always welcome 😄 
I'm holding on this one because we found a weird behaviour in long running (streaming) Spark runner applications that introduce an ever-increasing delay.
We've working on understanding this, and once we're done we will open tickets and provide patches - but we're still learning the problem.
I'm holding this change because it's directly in the path of any streaming Spark runner application - reading from `UnboundedSource` - so I don't want to introduce more "noise", and since this is an optimization, I don't find it urgent enough to merge ASAP.
@aviemzur knows the considerations since we work together, but I should have been more transparent and update here/JIRA about it.
